{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"font semantic tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"multiple","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"composite"}]},{"type":"text","text":" or not, and expose them."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllFontSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeFontSemanticTokensProvider\/init()"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeFontSemanticTokensProvider\/FontCompositeSemanticTokens-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeFontSemanticTokensProvider\/FontMultipleSemanticTokens-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeFontSemanticTokensProvider\/FontSemanticTokens-Implementations"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/AllFontSemanticTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/18OUDSTokensSemantic013FontCompositeB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/18OUDSTokensSemantic012FontMultipleB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/18